    <tr><th>19. Coumbian exchange
            <ol><li>What is it?</li>
                <li>How did it affect the Native Americans?</li>
                <li>How did it affect the Europeans?</li></ol></th>
        <td><u><b>a</b>. The Colombian Exchange is the economical and biological trade of goods between Europe and the Americas.<br><b>bi</b>. Lots of Native Americans died to disease and other factors<br><b>bii</b>. Lots of Native Americans were mistreated<br><b>ci</b>. Europe recieved a plethora of new goods<br><b>cii</b>. Europe profited massively because of the Colombian Exchange</td></u></tr>
